HEADWORD: Dichroite
<hw>Di"chro*ite</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Dichroism</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Min.)</fld> <def>Iolite; -- so called
